    "editable": false,
    "lead": "A very busy Term 2 so please note the following dates in your diary",
    "body": "<p>Monday 28th April: Term 2 Starts</p>\n\n<p>Tuesday 29th April: MNS Cross Country</p>\n\n<p>Monday 5th May: New Zealand Sign Language week</p>\n\n<p>Wednesday 14th May: Eastern Zone Cross Country</p>\n\n<p>Friday 16th May: Eastern Zone Cross Country PP</p>\n\n<p>Friday 16th May: Pink Shirt Day</p>\n\n<p>Friday 16th May: Mihi Whakatau</p>\n\n<p>Monday 19th May: NZ Playhouse - The Boy Who Cried Wolf</p>\n\n<p>Monday 19th May: Room 5 Pedal Ready</p>\n\n<p>Tuesday 20th May: Room 6 Pedal Ready</p>\n\n<p>Wednesday 21st May: Room 7 Pedal Ready</p>\n\n<p>Monday 26th May: Year 6 Group 1 Pedal Ready</p>\n\n<p>Tuesday 27th May: Parent Teacher Conferences</p>\n\n<p>Tuesday 27th May: Year 6 Group 1 Pedal Ready</p>\n\n<p>Wednesday 28th May: Eastern Zone Football</p>\n\n<p>Wednesday 28th May: Year 6 Group 2 Pedal Ready</p>\n\n<p>Thursday 29th May: Parent Teacher Conferences</p>\n\n<p>Thursday 29th May: Year 6 Group 2 Pedal Ready</p>\n\n<p>Monday 2nd June: Kings Birthday</p>\n\n<p>Monday 2nd June:  Pride in Schools Week</p>\n\n<p>Wednesday 4th June: Eastern Zone Football PP</p>\n\n<p>Tuesday 10th June: Inter Zone Cross Country</p>\n\n<p>Tuesday 10th June: Kōwhai Production 6pm</p>\n\n<p>Wednesday 11th June: Kōwhai Production Matinee 11am</p>\n\n<p>Thursday 12th June: Kōwhai Production 6pm</p>\n\n<p>Thursday 12th June: Pizza Day closes for ordering</p>\n\n<p>Thursday 12th June: Inter Zone Cross Country PP</p>\n\n<p>Monday 16th June: Term 2 Pizza Day</p>\n\n<p>Friday 20th June: Matariki Holiday</p>\n\n<p>Thursday 26th June: Eastern Zone Mini Ball</p>\n\n<p>Friday 27th June: End of Term 2</p>\n\n<p>Click here to see our full calendar: <a href=\"https://www.mns.school.nz/term-dates-calendar/\">https://www.mns.school.nz/term-dates-calendar/</a></p>",
