    "lead": "The Boy Who Cried Wolf - Monday 19th May",
    "body": "<p>We are very lucky to have the NZ Playhouse coming to perform to us this term.</p>\n\n<p>They will be performing 'The boy who cried wolf'.</p>\n\n<p>These plays are done by some very talented actors who bring a lot of humour to the show, as well as being educational.</p>\n\n<p>There will be singing, dancing and maybe some audience participation!</p>\n\n<p>We are asking for $7.00 per child to help towards the cost. This can be paid on <a href=\"https://shop.tgcl.co.nz/shop/q2.shtml?shop=Miramar%20North%20School&amp;service=reading_eggs\">Kindo.</a></p>",
