    "id": "8DBg8W3",
    "title": "Cross Country",
    "author": "Sarah Macintosh",
    "show_author": true,
    "editable": false,
    "lead": null,
    "body": "<p>After lots of practice and building of stamina, we got to run our cross country on Tuesday of Week 1.</p>\n\n<p>We enjoyed seeing our buddies run, plus older brothers and sisters of people in our class - and then it was our turn! We had lots of very excited students ready to go, after watching and cheering for the older kids. </p>\n\n<p>We started off by doing some stretches with our sports leaders, then lined up ready for the start sound. </p>\n\n<p>The teachers were so proud of everyone giving trying their best, and having a great attitude towards running the cross country - we know it's not everyone's favourite thing to do!</p>",
