    "body": "<p>On Pink Shirt Day, Friday 16th May 2025, Aotearoa will be transformed into a sea of māwhero/pink as we stand together to spread aroha, celebrate diversity and end bullying! Please donate directly through their website in support of the day and wear pink in support of the day if you can.&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://fundraise.pinkshirtday.org.nz/belinda-campbell\">https://fundraise.pinkshirtday.org.nz/belinda-campbell</a><br></p>\n\n<p>Kōrero Mai, Kōrero Atu, Mauri Tū, Mauri Ora – Speak Up, Stand Together, Stop Bullying!</p>",
